summary: You can find the spell in Riverwood Trader
descriptionHtml:
-The spell is in Riverwood Trader
-The spell knocks back targets and deals damage
-The images are real from the mod
-It doesn\'t have bugs
-The spell drains ( deals ) between 70 and 100 damage
- I don\'t think that there will be other versions . I am working on other spells .
-I hope you enjoy it
